snippet.title: Disney Tsum Tsum App Trailer | Disney
snippet.description:
Disney Tsum Tsum, published by LINE, is the fluffiest puzzle game ever! Collect, connect and pop Tsums based on your favorite Disney Tsum Tsum plushes. 
Find out more about Tsum Tsum: http://di.sn/chY

iOS: http://di.sn/pcC
Android: http://di.sn/ehl
